title: Eton TravelerIII AM/FM/LW Portable Radio Overview
description:
Eton Traveler III Black AM/FM/LW And Shortwave Portable Radio - TRAVELERIII- http://www.abt.com/product/81756/Eton-TRAVELERIII.html

Features
• AM/FM/LW/SW bands
• FM with RDS (Radio Data System)
• Automatic or manual digital tuning
• Auto tuning storage (ATS) function
• 500 memory stations
• Local/world time setting
• Sleep timer 
• Single alarm clock (by radio or buzzer)
• Snooze
• Rich orange LCD display
• Earphone jack (3.5mm)
• FM telescopic antenna
• Reset/lock function
• Power supply: Use USB cable (included) 4 AA batteries or 6V adapter (both sold separately)
